en_2125011_0	COLOMBO (News 1st) –  The final rites of the late Srima Dissanayake was held today (April 01).
en_2125011_1	The wife of one of the most prominent political figures in Sri Lanka passed away at a private hospital last Friday (March 29).
en_2125011_2	Srima Dissanayake, is the mother of Minister Naveen Dissanayake , MP Mayantha Dissanayake and Varuni Dissanayake.
en_2125011_3	President Maithripala Sirisena and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe paid their last respects to the deceased yesterday(March 31).
en_2125011_4	The funeral was held at the Borella public cemetery.
